  script_tag(name:"insight", value:"The following vulnerabilities exist:

  - CVE-2018-13289: An information exposure vulnerability in SYNO.FolderSharing.List allows remote
  attackers to obtain sensitive information via the (1) folder_path or (2) real_path parameter.

  - CVE-2018-13290: An information exposure vulnerability in SYNO.Core.ACL allows remote authenticated
  users to determine the existence of files or obtain sensitive information of files via the file_path
  parameter.

  - CVE-2018-13292: An information exposure vulnerability in /usr/syno/etc/mount.conf allows remote
  authenticated users to obtain sensitive information via the world readable configuration.");

  script_tag(name:"affected", value:"SRM version 1.1.x prior to 1.1.7-6941-2.");

  script_tag(name:"solution", value:"Update to firmware version 1.1.7-6941-2 or later.");

